	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "CIL 1(2).2, p. 764, no. 383 e. Grant (26) suggests the above identification with the Praetor of 67 or 68." .
